1
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:12,100
The rules of the Heavenly Dao are so tyrannical.

2
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:16,360
The life and death of all things are strictly bound by it.

3
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,640
For cultivators like us,

4
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,930
what room is there left for choice?

5
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,940
Do not speak nonsense.

6
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:26,240
The ways of this world

7
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:30,890
were established only after enduring thousands of tribulations.

8
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:34,540
It is not for you to casually judge right from wrong.

9
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:36,840
High God,

10
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:39,940
have you never doubted the Heavenly Dao?

11
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:45,560
Never.

12
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:58,760
Come.

13
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,480
Drink this tea.

14
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:05,040
If becoming an immortal means cutting off all emotions,

15
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:11,500
then I'd rather be reverted to my original form.

16
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,020
Among these emotions,

17
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:26,880
who exactly is it that you cannot forget?

18
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,000
I'm afraid

19
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,410
of forgetting the longing in my heart.

20
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:38,640
To me,

21
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,040
on this lonely, difficult,

22
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:43,170
centuries-long path of cultivation,

23
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:46,770
he is exceptionally precious.

24
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:02,440
Drink it.

25
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,700
I will help you keep this longing.

26
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:14,280
Drink it now.

27
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,200
Thank you, Immortal.

28
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:56,600
Go.

29
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,480
Deity.

30
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:10,680
Deity.

31
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,600
Deity.

32
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:25,800
Break.

33
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:50,210
Your reaction shows you clearly know her.

34
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:52,800
I know her.

35
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:54,840
What happened to her?

36
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,360
Ancestor, this is the mortal realm.

37
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:59,320
There's no shame in romance.

38
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,720
Nonsense.

39
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,930
Get to the point.

40
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:06,080
A century after you descended to the mortal realm,

41
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:08,680
which is just a few years in the immortal realm.

42
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:10,760
Bai Jingqing

43
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:14,940
voluntarily resigned her immortal post and came to the mortal realm.

44
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:20,560
Why would she want to start over?

45
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:22,880
Everything is predestined.

46
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:24,880
This was her choice

47
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:27,040
and her karma.

48
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,480
Ancestor.

49
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:33,919
I think

50
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,840
that is her karma.

51
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:44,400
At that time,

52
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,520
it was indeed my fault.

53
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:50,480
An immortal should not be moved by pity.

54
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,400
But all things in the past

55
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:53,680
are gone.

56
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:01,280
What does this have to do with Feilu?

57
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:03,040
This Feilu

58
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:07,600
is the reincarnation of Bai Jingqing.

59
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,000
I understand.

60
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:15,840
You may leave.

61
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:20,810
Then, Ancestor,

62
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,090
I will take my leave.

63
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:16,460
Greetings, immortal friend.

64
00:10:17,640 --> 00:10:18,960
I am Baili Lingfeng,

65
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:21,920
and my duty is to guard the Zhexian Terrace.

66
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:24,810
People often say that destiny makes fools of men.

67
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,560
I know a little bit about

68
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:28,770
the reason for your departure.

69
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:32,840
If you are trying to persuade me,

70
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,880
then save your breath.

71
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,400
Immortal friend.

72
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,540
High God Qingxuan,

73
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:41,600
formed from a single thought over ten thousand years,

74
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,240
took shape from that thought.

75
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,480
His Dao heart is extremely resolute,

76
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:46,280
as indestructible as a diamond.

77
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:50,760
And he has guarded the Sanshan Stream in the Heaven Realm for tens of thousands of years.

78
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:53,840
His actions and thoughts have their own Dao to follow.

79
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:55,740
But if you leave this time,

80
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:57,700
won't it be a tribulation for you?

81
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,080
I remind you,

82
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:02,280
if you descend to the mortal realm,

83
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:04,010
you will lose all your memories

84
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,840
and all your magical powers.

85
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:08,400
Whether you become a human or a beast

86
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:10,680
is yet unknown.

87
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:12,340
High God Qingxuan.

88
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:13,840
You know him?

89
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,940
We just have some ties of destiny.

90
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,880
Where is he now?

91
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:21,620
If it's meant to be,

92
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:23,500
you will definitely meet.

93
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:30,560
Xiaoxiao.

94
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:37,500
He looks exactly like you.

95
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:38,640
Good boy.

96
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,650
Your name will be Feilu.

97
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:41,960
Chen Feilu.

98
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:43,040
Feilu.

99
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:44,640
Good name.

100
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:45,880
Feilu.

101
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:14,540
Why did it change back?

102
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:16,400
The talisman isn't working.

103
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:18,860
Didn't the master say his goods are genuine?

104
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:40,810
What are you looking at,

105
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:42,080
Master?

106
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:48,800
Pingjie Qianghaihui.
